name: Women's adidas Nova Run X Shoes
description: Being comfortable on your run is just as important as winning the race. These shoes combine soft, supportive Cloudfoam cushioning with a durable Adiwear outsole for comprehensive control and an energised ride. The mesh upper features a foot-hugging, no-sew fit for a locked-in feel.
